	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">社区里有这样一块“任意球场”，不愁没有地方打球了</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-16 15:35:46 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">7</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">48</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

